# Frontend Environment Variables

## Local Development
```bash
REACT_APP_API_URL=http://localhost:5000/api
```

## Production (Railway)
```bash
REACT_APP_API_URL=https://your-backend-url.railway.app/api
```

## Notes

- **REACT_APP_API_URL**: Must include /api suffix
- Frontend build-time variable, not runtime (set before `npm run build`)
- Railway will provide backend URL after deploy
- Update this, rebuild, and redeploy frontend if backend URL changes
